'''彭纳马省'''（Penama）是[[瓦努阿图|瓦努阿图]]的一个[[省|省]]，包含[[奥巴岛|奥巴岛]]（{{lang|en|Aoba}}／{{lang|en|Ambae}}）、[[迈沃岛|迈沃岛]]（{{lang|en|Maewo}}）、[[彭特科斯特岛|彭特科斯特岛]]（{{lang|en|Pentecost}}）等[[岛屿|岛屿]]。彭纳马（{{lang|en|Penama}}）一词来源于岛屿彭特科斯特岛（{{lang|en|Pentecost}}）、奥巴岛（{{lang|en|Aoba}}／{{lang|en|Ambae}}）与迈沃岛（{{lang|en|Maewo}}）的合写。该省人口28,960<ref>[http://www.governmentofvanuatu.gov.vu/index.php/publicationdocuments/vanuatu-statistics 2009 Census Summary release final] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131221233814/http://www.governmentofvanuatu.gov.vu/index.php/publicationdocuments/vanuatu-statistics |date=2013-12-21 }} - Government of Vanuatu</ref>，面积1,198km².

该省[[首府|省会]]为[[隆阿纳|隆阿纳]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://volcano.si.edu/volcano.cfm?vn=257030 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2022-02-03 |archive-date=2021-05-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210507060438/https://volcano.si.edu/volcano.cfm?vn=257030 }}</ref>

